00:06:14.000 --> 00:06:18.000
you want to be sure that it's going to be around for a while.

00:06:19.000 --> 00:06:22.000
You want to be sure that when there is a problem,

00:06:22.000 --> 00:06:25.000
that there is a community that can help you,

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:29.000
or maybe even other developers that can answer questions,

